      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You have got to see this beauty in person\u2014it is honestly an absolute dream! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and sparkling clean. It looks and drives exactly like it just rolled off the showroom floor. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Shoot me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 44900.0,
