    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that has been preserved with obsessive care. This car looks and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely no rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks, protected by a recently applied professional ceramic coating. The wheels are pristine with zero curb rash, wrapped in high-performance tires with near-full tread. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and matte, free of any bolster wear or creasing, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car scent. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the ambient lighting, functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been stored in a climate-controlled garage and serviced exclusively at the dealership\u2014I have the complete binder of service records to prove it. This is a rare find for a buyer who demands perfection and wants a vehicle that needs absolutely nothing but a new home.",
      "price": 48200.0,
